    "Our approach and the corresponding prompts will be discussed more precisely in Section IV.",
    "Lifting Message Grammars: Quality and DiversityWe ask the LLM to provide machine-readable information about the message structure (i.e., the grammar), and we evaluate the quality of the generated grammars and the diversity of message types covered w.r.t. the ground truth.",
    "To establish the ground-truth grammar, two authors spent a total of 8 hours in reading the RFC 2326, and manually and individually extracting the corresponding grammar with the perfect agreement.",
